  "text": "We recently proposed a novel approach for predicting malaria transmission in houses within a limited area based on ecological and environmental characteristics [CITATION_1] . We demonstrated that a regression model including spatial and time-dependent variables at the village and house levels yields a spatiotemporal prediction of malaria transmission comparable to that obtained on the basis of entomological data [CITATION_2] .",
